{"tid":1913290,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"韓國TWICE出寫真《 You only live ONCE 》短裙晒腿玩復古風 9款封底照任君選擇","createTime":"2020-03-06T16:04:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-07T07:52:01.000Z","uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1ea48022e100c32ed5d58c866bf04c3a02d2f87b","tid":1913290,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T16:04:41.000Z","msg":"寫真界戰場不止是日本女星的天下，近日韓國的人 氣組合TWICE就推出久違了兩年的新寫真集《 You only live ONCE》，九名TWICE成員分別擔任了九款寫真集封底女郎，粉絲可以因應 各自喜好來選購寫真集，忠粉會不會9款都入手？<br />\n<br />\n今次TWICE推出的新寫真集，是由韓國《 D-icon》雜誌所推出的第七本韓星寫真集，書名《 You only live ONCE》，取自TWICE對粉絲的稱呼「ONCE」，封面上有九位成員：子瑜、Momo、Sana、 Mina、志效、定延、娜璉、多賢和彩瑛的大合照，封底則有九款她們各自的單人照，並將分別推出日文和韓文版本，當中還附送了以各個成 員為主題的相卡、文件夾、座枱月曆，以及由成員們親手所寫的祝福賀卡等，非常豐富。不過由於寫真集在寒冷的冬季拍攝，各成員的衣著都相對較為密實，但其中也有不少大玩復古風格和以短裙晒腿的造型，展現出她們華麗又型格的一面。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.weekendhk.com/1022858/weekspecial/entertainment/twice-%e5%af%ab%e7%9c%9f-plt/2/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.weekendhk.com%2F1022858%2Fweekspecial%2Fentertainment%2Ftwice-%25e5%25af%25ab%25e7%259c%259f-plt%2F2%2F&d=nExaWN1d7lalHJLKFoHQnH4WTS3z8ocQ7DCXl2btf88%3D&h=2a973af5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.weekendhk.com/1022858/weekspecial/entertainment/twice-%e5%af%ab%e7%9c%9f-plt/2/</a>"},{"pid":"7692a86e8f4c30fe73f77044e343df06edcc17d8","tid":1913290,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T16:05:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imgs.weekendhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/a1_1161a_west_3688248755e61ec14475b2-800x446.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.weekendhk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F03%2Fa1_1161a_west_3688248755e61ec14475b2-800x446.jpg&h=65b4048d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.weekendhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/a3_1161a_west_9113339345e61ec1861391-800x545.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.weekendhk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F